{"tid":1817501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Liang zhen ying 批黃色經濟圈幼稚：你們就是「中国製造」!　","createTime":"2020-01-09T06:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T08:21:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"caa0270fec4c89859324187b14562b55357bf46a","tid":1817501,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"反修例運動中，不少示威者提倡建立「黃色經濟圈」，光顧支持示威活動的商舖，全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英今日（9日）在Facebook發文，批評「黃色經濟圈」幼稚，指「黃店」離不開「中國製造」，年輕人及其父母亦同樣是「中國製造」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3827605/org/17923c73cd274fca471a7da779cd2041.png/9ThPEcUOWmLPQUlWyDmVM17BR-XKhaQZb3vRwW970cE?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3827605%2Forg%2F17923c73cd274fca471a7da779cd2041.png%2F9ThPEcUOWmLPQUlWyDmVM17BR-XKhaQZb3vRwW970cE%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=c81465d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁振英：姓名皆是中文字 身體水分主要是東江水<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在帖文中提及一家黃色網店「重光號」，標榜所有販售產品均非中國製造，他認為香港人就是「中國製造」，「你們的姓、名都是中文字，你們身體的水分主要是東江水」，市民的日常生活所使用的東西同樣是中國製造，例如東江水、水泥鋼筋。他又指，香港每年有三至四成中港新婚夫婦，反映中國無論是人、文化或產品都已滲入港人生活。<br />\n<br />\n他以蘇格蘭和北愛爾蘭作例，指兩國鬧分離但不會「幼稚至搞什麼自己人的經濟圈」，形容建立「黃色經濟圈」是幼稚行為，並著年輕人要帶眼帶腦識人，「（壹傳媒創辦人）黎智英的子女只會做正常生意，不會入黃色經濟圈。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/419583/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E6%89%B9%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0</code></pre>"},{"pid":"09c29c2cf83bd9475796413bb336e382fbaddcbf","tid":1817501,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ccf6e63490032372a4b9995fcd0b5adc54904d4","tid":1817501,"uid":154106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"我呀公呀婆，呀爺呀媽係 中華民國制造，父母香港制造，中咩野國？中華民國好地地仲係到"},{"pid":"15122cc34b516b7925f89dd7e88cb65b16972e59","tid":1817501,"uid":263213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"港英製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n振英洗唔洗改自己個名做振中啊"},{"pid":"08d07cdc8e449d0d1823c304b51f1397bf4f05d7","tid":1817501,"uid":276865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"日本人姓名都係漢字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb83686eb620972aa499bcf71aaa0ebbe6996c2","tid":1817501,"uid":193215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢係唔係想推非獨派轉軚支持港獨姐，不愧為港獨之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6f0704e5de8105d4f7d13e4f38b98aa5e20207","tid":1817501,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"你為甚麼就離不開美國製造的facebook"},{"pid":"87abb5cbba923dfd61f5ae59158a684803d854c3","tid":1817501,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"佢英國製造"},{"pid":"dfe528f6350e8edfc1657ad0640f645301c886c8","tid":1817501,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:23:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我全家都係加拿大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5b16f0756448f8bd1d2c1d28b760117b37cc57","tid":1817501,"uid":293504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"60,70,80後出生都是港英時代<br />\n是英國製造"},{"pid":"bf242090a63325293211bac9ebba1458505389c9","tid":1817501,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"愛國不愛黨 完"},{"pid":"970c8beab2b4310da20e4f27cba76349300b7c